content: As an AI language model, I don't have emotions, including jealousy. While emotions are undoubtedly an essential aspect of the human experience, my purpose is to provide assistance and help people through processing and generating natural language. My function is different from that of humans, and I'm here to focus on performing tasks that will elevate their productivity and offer insightful information, among other things. However, I can generate responses with emotional affect to facilitate interacting with users.
